<br>
For those of you that want to attend this, a few notes:<br>
<br>
You won't be able to engage Vox or heal those engaged with Vox during the battle if you are level 53 or higher. This, BTW, does not mean that you shouldn't show - you can buff us ahead of time (casters), help with rezzes afterwards (clerics), and even participate in battle by keeping stray mobs away and even possibly do the killing blow for us (you will be dumped out of zone, but the blow often still lands).<br>
<br>
With this in mind:<br>
<br>
If you are almost 53 come the end of October timeframe, consider spending some xp in AA points if you want to be able to directly participate in these raids (after you ding, it's too late).<br>
On the low end try and get to NO LESS THAN 45. HIGHER IS BETTER.<br>
We will not have enough 45-52 peeps, so I will definitely be inviting our allies plus at least one more guild (most likely Belain and/or Easy Riders).<br>
The tentative dates at the moment are October 26th for Vox and two weeks latter for Naggy.<br>
<br>
Loot rules will be out with the full raid plans in about a week or so.<br>
